description:
My HoneyDew this week on the first episode from the new HoneyDew Studio is none other than Mystic Rick himself, Tom Segura! Tom and I reminisce about our early, embarrassing years with girls and just how awkward and stupid we really were and honestly, still are. Make sure you subscribe to my YouTube channel & watch The Dew there every toozdee!

If you want more weekly HoneyDew, subscribe to The HoneyDew with Y’all, my new Patreon show where I highlight the lowlights with y’all! If you or someone you know has a HoneyDew story that’s worth hearing, send an email with a brief summary of your story to HoneyDewpodcast@gmail.com

https://TheHoneyDewPodcast.com
